{"tid":2172420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港製造創本土環保貓砂「希望為香港出分力」","createTime":"2020-08-24T14:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T21:17:42.000Z","uid":221437,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"95f88140001e21e35e3c45cebf72f7354e9e799e","tid":2172420,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:57:20.000Z","msg":"「Green Paws六斗」是香港第一間，亦是唯一一間環保木貓砂工廠。老闆Kelvin是回流港人，中學時到了澳洲讀書，畢業後原本在當地做建築室內設計，但心裏始終記掛香港，兩年之前就毅然返回香港從低做起。「一開始是想返回香港出一分力カ，當時就想做甚麼可以幫到香港呢，後來發現木回收在香港幾乎沒人做，就決定投資這個行業。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n根據過往的統計數字，香港每天大概浪費超過600噸的廢木，當中有不少是用作物流搬運工具的木卡板，Kelvin的工廠就以回收木卡板為主。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/8J7hN_lQt5g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F8J7hN_lQt5g&d=HUgUlm9NWlnA9xfyBh3Sbgy1DEY80m5I9K8mtjxpzv8%3D&h=54c3862b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/8J7hN_lQt5g</a>"},{"pid":"84f638d5e39d2f6ff4c13fbc5110f61a7f68f39a","tid":2172420,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T14:57:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"0717a8698681838791a3e4d63d262333ce54bf8f","tid":2172420,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:01:31.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"0e0c161b93fb641f8f261220f0a9cb8175698142","tid":2172420,"uid":221437,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:01:33.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3c8c254a598241183c1139b8b6e4ad2d1de1b21a","tid":2172420,"uid":74083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9446221fdb854802d8463c2ca6b425486115524","tid":2172420,"uid":118120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T15:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=